<taxonomicName id="AD5AA302680337745D58FEF678F1F2C9" class="Insecta" family="Acrididae" genus="Parga" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Parga" order="Orthoptera" pageId="47" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Parga</taxonomicName>
Walker, 1870: 504 (replacement for 
<taxonomicName id="40AC5A26DD6818FD0598D5D6E249D440" class="Arachnida" family="Acrididae" genus="Amycus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Amycus" order="Orthoptera" pageId="47" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Amycus</taxonomicName>
