<taxonomicName id="2D51DB05E629C5C929D58FB9E0ECB7AA" genus="P." lsidName="P. xanthoptera" pageId="47" pageNumber="84" rank="species" species="xanthoptera">P. xanthoptera</taxonomicName>
but differs in having proportionately longer and narrower antennae (Fig. 350).
</paragraph>
